            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Neutron-rich copper isotopes were produced by means of",
                " proton- or neutron-induced fission reactions on 238U.",
                " After the production, 77Cu was selectively laser",
                " ionized, mass separated, and sent to different",
                " detection systems."
              ]
            }
          ],
